00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:51,520
y a los argentinos
nos va a ir cada vez peor.

262
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:54,600
Entonces se toman
decisiones equivocadas,

263
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,440
